    • Constructor Detail

      • FileGeneratorAsync

        public FileGeneratorAsync(OnTaskCompleteListener listener,
                          java.lang.String pathToFile,
                          @NonNull
                          java.lang.String data,
                          java.lang.String nameOfFile)
        Generate a file via an asynchronous call. Runs on background thread and passes the data back upon the passed listener
        Parameters:
        listener - Listener to pass back OnTaskCompleteListener
        pathToFile - The path to the file. If null, will write to downloads
        data - The data to be written. Cannot be null
        nameOfFile - The name of the file. If null, will be auto-generated as PGMacUtilities_ + the date in epoch (long) time
